PRO AUGMENTED INTELIGENCE ROBOTS

Programmable robots integrated with human which separated from core controller.
Autonomous robots have powerful processors and can perform actions and make decisions without human intervention.
It depends on your imagination but I have a lot of imaginary robotic friends that want to make a world a better place as human just keep doing violence, war, racism, .... 
So follow my work to meet my amazing imaginary friends.
